ve Tubes was transferred into 50 ml tubes and made up to the 15 ml mark with PBS (without Ca2+ and Mg2+)<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"html":null,"section":null,"section_color":"","section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":1044116,"guid":"8EAA583004A711EBB5E0CB942A9565C7","previous_id":1044115,"previous_guid":"8EA7E73004A711EBB5E0CB942A9565C7","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"A84CD7E109624D4F886FD97F0DDC96F9","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":""}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"76D193F75E954BAC8618353314CCF699","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">- this was transferred to the filter of the OncoQuick tube.<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"html":null,"section":null,"section_color":"","section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":1044117,"guid":"8EAC2CF004A711EBB5E0CB942A9565C7","previous_id":1044116,"previous_guid":"8EAA583004A711EBB5E0CB942A9565C7","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"0C56F638172A4566B41483778278902B","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":""}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"46213721F1A041D7912C7008B2BC9E9E","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">- Centrifuge this OncoQuick tube for 20 minutes at 1600g and +4 \u00b0C. The acceleration as well as the deceleration of the centrifuge were set to level five (medium) as specified by greiner bio one. The pipette and a 50 ml tube were moistened with the FACS buffer to minimize the binding of tumor cells to the walls of these materials. This step was also called \"pre-wetting\".<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"html":null,"section":null,"section_color":"","section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":1044118,"guid